title: Hour 1: Mile High Mistake?
description:
In this episode, Stephen A., Chris "Mad Dog" Russo, and Keyshawn Johnson debate whether or not Russell Wilson is the most disappointing player in the NFL after a poor performance against the Chargers. Plus, should we be more concerned with the offensive struggles in Green Bay or in Tampa? Two teams are back in the New York groove, but which one has a better shot at the playoffs: Jets or Giants? Tim Legler joins the show to debate if the suspension of Celtics head coach Ime Udoka will keep the team from reaching a second-straight finals.
